{"type": "article", "id": 13936, "title": "相互支撑的衣架", "description": "", "date": "2015-08-25T07:33:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122444fJTRe3YzwN9F2BWc.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这是来自希腊雅典的设计师 Yiannis Ghikas 的一个衣架作品，整个衣架由相互独立又相互支撑的三个部分组成，就像名字 “Game of Trust” 一样，让人想到背对背战斗的朋友——相互支撑和信任，把背后的敌人留给你。而组成的作品稳固简洁，非常赏心悦目。<a href=\"http://www.yiannisghikas.com/?page_id=111\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看 Yiannis Ghikas 更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141616BWZFlCD4VjhtnKi0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141617TgPv7Mdf4k2Qar9s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141618CnZmhVHq04wy8e2R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141618N4RHvbrtB6jLqP9Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}